body:
`equals` has the following syntax:

```javascript
{
   $search: {
      "index": <index name>, // optional, defaults to "default"
      "equals": {
         "path": "<field-to-search>",
         "value": <boolean-value>|<objectId>|<number>|<date>|<string>,
         "score": <score-options>
      }
   }
}
```
